{
  "stem": "6526.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanna-- I wanna-- At least, I wanna go back with a friend of mine that we were together, or to take my wife along.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my wife is not a traveler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And especially in this respect, you know, she's, uh, very touchy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She doesn't wanna go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, uh, I hope-- I hope to have, uh-- to go back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, by then, I guess [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, uh, I would like to go back to Auschwitz to see how it is there, because I-- I can visualize.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can draw the map of where things were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I can--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just after the war, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, at the moment, I don't, uh, recall anything more to add.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unless something-- uh, you see someone, or something comes, uh, about-- about torching-- about-- about the lamp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, oh, that lamp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something has happened with the lamp, and I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing that I recall to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, uh--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what advice?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The younger generation knows the-- the story of World War II.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what kind of advice you want me to give them?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To-- to see that no such regime [SOBBING] ever happens in any place of the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the advice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Especially when today we have, in-- in-- in Yugoslavia and Serbia that it happens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, I feel with the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I feel with the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you'll ask me why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because-- cause the Serbs are the underdogs in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Croats and the Germans were like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- the Bosnians-- I mean, the-- the Muslims, I don't know about them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Croats were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Serbs h-- helped all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this is-- uh, those that don't feel, uh, what the-- the Serbs went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
